#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:1
msgid "Care plans and vital signs"
msgstr "Plans de soins et signes vitaux"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:4
msgid ""
"Care plans, daily care schedule, vital signs entry and trends, and nursing "
"notes in Resthome."
msgstr ""
"Plans de soins, planning des soins du jour, saisie des signes vitaux et "
"tendances, notes infirmières dans Resthome."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:7
msgid ""
"Beyond medication, the Care app organizes **day-to-day nursing work**: care "
"plans, scheduling, vital signs and notes."
msgstr ""
"Au-delà de la médication, l'application Soins organise le **travail "
"infirmier au quotidien** : plans de soins, planning, signes vitaux et notes."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:9
msgid "Care plans"
msgstr "Plans de soins"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:11
msgid ""
"A **care plan** describes the **goals** of a resident's care and the actions"
" to carry out. It follows a clear cycle:"
msgstr ""
"Un **plan de soins** décrit les **objectifs** de prise en charge d'un "
"résident et les actions à mener. Il suit un cycle clair :"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:13
msgid "**Activate** — the plan becomes effective."
msgstr "**Activer** — le plan devient effectif."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:14
msgid "**Put under review** then **Validate review** — periodic reassessment."
msgstr ""
"**Mettre en revue** puis **Valider la revue** — réévaluation périodique."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:15
msgid "**Complete** / **Cancel** — closure."
msgstr "**Terminer** / **Annuler** — clôture."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:17
msgid "Each plan carries its own **goals**, which makes follow-up measurable."
msgstr "Chaque plan porte ses **objectifs**, ce qui rend le suivi mesurable."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:19
msgid "Care scheduling"
msgstr "Planning des soins"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:21
msgid "**Today's care** — the list of care tasks to perform today."
msgstr "**Soins du jour** — la liste des soins à réaliser aujourd'hui."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:22
msgid "**My assigned care** — what is assigned to you personally."
msgstr "**Mes soins assignés** — ce qui vous revient personnellement."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:23
msgid ""
"Each scheduled care task can be **started**, **completed**, **cancelled** or"
" marked **missed** — the round stays traceable."
msgstr ""
"Chaque soin planifié se **démarre**, se **termine**, s'**annule** ou se "
"marque **manqué** — la tournée reste traçable."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:25
msgid "Vital signs"
msgstr "Signes vitaux"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:27
msgid "From the resident record, open **Vital signs entry**."
msgstr "Depuis la fiche du résident, ouvrez **Saisie des signes vitaux**."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:28
msgid ""
"Fill in the measurements (blood pressure, pulse, temperature, weight, "
"saturation…)."
msgstr ""
"Renseignez les mesures (tension, pouls, température, poids, saturation…)."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:29
msgid "**Save.**"
msgstr "**Enregistrez.**"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:31
msgid "Trends"
msgstr "Tendances"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:34
msgid ""
"The **Trends** tool displays how vital signs evolve over time — handy for "
"spotting a deterioration before it sets in."
msgstr ""
"L'outil **Tendances** affiche l'évolution des signes vitaux dans le temps — "
"pratique pour repérer une dégradation avant qu'elle ne s'installe."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:37
msgid "Nursing notes"
msgstr "Notes infirmières"

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:39
msgid ""
"**Nursing notes** record observations. Items that need attention surface "
"under **Watch points** / **Attention required**, and are marked **resolved**"
" once handled."
msgstr ""
"Les **notes infirmières** consignent les observations. Les points qui "
"demandent attention remontent dans **Points de vigilance** / **Attention "
"requise**, et se marquent **résolus** une fois traités."

#: ../../content/soins/plans-de-soins.md:41
msgid "Learn more"
msgstr "Pour aller plus loin"

